Title: An Act Changing the Name of Tangalan Elementary School in the Municipality of Tangalan, Province of Aklan, to Justice Jose Hontiveros Memorial Elementary School
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 671
An Act Changing the Name of Tangalan Elementary School in the Municipality of Tangalan, Province of Aklan, to Justice Jose Hontiveros Memorial Elementary School
Section 1. The name of the Tangalan Elementary School in the Municipality of Tangalan, Province of Aklan, is changed to Justice Hontiveros Memorial Elementary School.1avvphi1
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: March 7, 1984
